Package gw.api.team

Class TeamExposureFilterSet

java.lang.Object
gw.api.filters.FilterSetBase
gw.api.exposure.ExposureFilterSetBase
gw.api.exposure.OwnedRelatedExposureFilterSetBase
gw.api.team.TeamExposureFilterSet
Direct Known Subclasses:
TeamGroupExposureFilterSet, TeamOtherExposureFilterSet, TeamPendingExposureFilterSet, TeamUserExposureFilterSet
public abstract class TeamExposureFilterSet extends OwnedRelatedExposureFilterSetBase
Filter set for the TeamExposures list view.

For the group and user action types the action returns all exposures and the filters do all the work. They apply a "pre filter" - either exposures owned by the user/group or related to the user/group - and then apply a further filter (such as Open, New etc) on top of that pre filter.

For the pending assign and other action types the action filters down to the pending assign/other exposures for the group and the filters just add the further filters. So for these action types the pre filter is null.

Not all of the filters are appropriate for all the action types so the methods isClosedFilterEnabled() and isRelatedFiltersEnabled() are provided to enable/disble the filters that only apply to specific types.
